  "description": "Alterations including erection of mansard roof extension to main rear roof and extension above part of three-storey back addition; formation of roof terrace above remainder of back addition with 1.7m high screening. Works in connection with conversion of upper floor flat into 1 x 3-bedroom and 2 x 1-bedroom flats.",
